title: Turkish Delight - Christian J.  [prog/electro house]
description:
---==Turkish Delight==---

         by
     Christian J


A delightful stream of beats moving from rugged, middle-eastern electro house thru deep progressive house.  Totally underground mix, give it a whack if you wanna hear something that just rocks the set.


Tracks from Sharam Jey, James Harcourt, Dubfire, Marc Romboy, Stephan Bodzin, and many more 

If you are a fan of Global Underground mixes, try this out for size
